{"tid":36674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"﻿南港島線無人駕駛列車僅三卡 憂難疏導人潮","createTime":"2016-12-13T00:38:37.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T06:00:51.000Z","uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b180aa7b1f23ece80b861f7d7b4ba7e89e69788f","tid":36674,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T00:38:37.000Z","msg":"﻿南港島線僅三卡 憂難疏導人潮<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/daily/hk/522714/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fdaily%2Fhk%2F522714%2F&d=wwMw%2Fw%2BpA6kMX3rRC10fwwT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=e79463a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fdaily%2Fhk%2F522714%2F&h=702d8ec5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/daily/hk/522714/</a>"},{"pid":"b593453a2c5d6dac0c8052ccb72753ef1e99de1a","tid":36674,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T00:42:20.000Z","msg":"2012年4月16日，港鐵召開記者會，宣佈已向長春軌道客車購入10列3卡南港島綫無人駕駛列車，合共30卡，外型以及車廂設計近似市區綫同款車。法國MBD設計事務所負責列車內部設計，中國北車長客負責外部設計以及製造。&nbsp;長春軌道客車則稱其後港鐵於2011年7月增訂10列3卡車廂列車，供南港島綫使用。"},{"pid":"91e9c048930ba99bed0a9b843cc00fdc85178f92","tid":36674,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T00:44:11.000Z","msg":"現時月台的設計缺乏增設卡車的彈性，恐將來要額外興建隧道。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd9497eb860941dab9661c7a75a996379fbda0ca","tid":36674,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T00:48:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>現時月台的設計缺乏增設卡車的彈性，恐將來要額外興建隧道。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n記者過慮咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d93eeefcec391b9df2c4f3c6bfa44979f5feef5","tid":36674,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T01:37:35.000Z","msg":"日日同海怡D OL迫沙典魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},